          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                " 90Sr-Cl2 standardized solution, equivalent to",
                " 3.7 x 10**2 kBq was pipetted into the bottom of high-",
                " purity quartz tube 8 mm inner diam, 100 mm length. A",
                " 40 kBq 85Sr-Cl2 standardized solution was added in the",
                " same manner. After drying of the solution, the quartz",
                " tube was welded under evacuation. The welded tube was",
                " circa 20 mm in length. This tube was put into alumin.",
                " capsule and then housed in the irradiation capsule.",
                " The loss of 85Sr was checked by the radioactivity of",
                " 514-keV gamma line emitted from 85Sr",
                " Monitor samples were Co/Al alloy wire 0.381 mm diam,",
                " cobalt content 0,46wt%, and",
                " Au/Al alloy wire 0.510 mm diam, gold content 0.112wt%."
              ]
            }
          ],
